### 1) Lấy danh sách users theo role
GET {{base}}/api/users?role=manager
###
GET {{base}}/api/users?role=teacher
###
GET {{base}}/api/users?role=student

### 2) Tạo center (dán ManagerId GUID từ bước 0)
POST {{base}}/api/centers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "centerName": "UIT Center",
  "managerId": "7cc7aaa4-f172-42f7-affc-8873872c4b4b",
  "centerAddress": "123 Dien Bien Phu",
  "phone": "0900000000",
  "centerEmail": "hello@uit-center.edu",
  "logo": null,
  "isActive": true
}

### 3) Tạo subject (dán CenterId từ bước 2)
POST {{base}}/api/subjects
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "subjectName": "Mathematics 10",
  "centerId": "bc9edad7-e48c-4fc6-b676-fe5c268dccef",
  "gradeLevel": "G10"
}

### 4) Kiểm tra Subjects & Grades
GET {{base}}/api/subjects?centerId=bc9edad7-e48c-4fc6-b676-fe5c268dccef
###
GET {{base}}/api/grades?centerId=bc9edad7-e48c-4fc6-b676-fe5c268dccef

